{
    "version": 5,
    "bundle": "XJU6MLKCSG6Q3C4HHLSDOIWPZ564QBKQ",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "041047001",
    "title": "それは叙事詩にも似て",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "一閃の光芒が、地平を切り拓くのを見た。",
            "enText": "A flash of light cut through the horizon.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "pathId": -3416195965016129840,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "顔もわからないほど遠くを駆けているのに、\n息遣いまで聞こえるようで。",
            "enText": "Even though they were running so far away that I couldn't make \nout their face, I could still hear their breath.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "pathId": -7610609840876999785,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "その走りは荒々しく、必死で、しかし誇り高く。\n先陣を往くさまは、まるで――",
            "enText": "They were running wildly and desperately, but still filled with \npride. The way they were forging ahead, it was almost like―",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "……英雄……",
                    "enText": "……A hero……",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4445334100090122225,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "名前も顔も知らない彼女の走りをもう1度見たくて、\n正体を突き止めようと探してはみたけれど――",
            "enText": "Even though I didn't know her name or her face, \nI wanted to see her run again. Even though I \nhad searched, I still couldn't find her――",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "pathId": -9165917017949032512,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……結局、名前の最初の1字も掴めないまま数か月が経った。",
            "enText": "……In the end, even after months of searching, I still couldn't \nfind out what her name was, let alone anything else about her.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "pathId": 6118400236072823772,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "あの『英雄』のことばかり考えていたら英雄譚が読みたくなって、\nよさそうな伝記を探しに来たのだが……なかなか見つからない。",
            "enText": "Since I couldn't think of anything but that 『Hero』, it made me \nwant to read a heroic tale. I came looking for a suitable \nbiography…… but I just can't seem to find them.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 123,
            "pathId": -7744505625179955884,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "？？？",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……あ、あの……なにか、お困りでしょうか？",
            "enText": "……U-um…… can I help you with anything?",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 227,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "君は……？",
                    "enText": "You are……?",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "貴方は……？",
                    "enText": "You are……?",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 181,
                    "pathId": -7899545404115818009
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": -5438815910595390383
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7686282284683932833,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "ぜ、ゼンノロブロイです。図書委員、なので……！\nその、本を探されているならお力になれるかなって……。",
            "enText": "Z-Zenno Rob Roy. T-the librarian……! \nUm, if you're looking for a book, I thought I could help……",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 386,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 378,
                    "pathId": -8015872316870751201
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -8878865948049759518
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8609877759806897913,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "あっ、ご、ご迷惑だったらごめんなさいっ！",
            "enText": "Ah, I-I'm sorry if I'm bothering you!",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 128,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "じゃあ……伝記ってどこにあるかな？",
                    "enText": "Then…… where are the biographies?",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 133,
                    "pathId": 7497934114864365688
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -8831857663745998268
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7115351001646907325,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "伝記……！　たしかに、わかりづらいところにありますよねっ。\n実は歴史書じゃなくて、小説とエッセイの棚に置いてあるんです。",
            "enText": "Biographies……! Now that I think about it, they're in a place \nthat's kind of confusing. You won't find them under history, \nthey're with the essays and novels.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 368,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 169,
                    "pathId": 5425425240831034171
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 113,
                    "pathId": 2528109711028571313
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6309369891293512504,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "ほら、伝記ってフィクションが混ざっていることも多いので。\nそういうものを史実と混同しないようにって、別けてるそうですよ。",
            "enText": "You see, biographies often have a lot of fiction \nmixed in. So they're not confused with historical \nfacts, they were separated it seems.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 341,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 213,
                    "pathId": -951108614502542723
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -915662181425004655
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3409603542079739936,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "あ、でも私はフィクションが混ざっているところも好きですよ！\n逸話が創作されるのは、後世での評価が高い証拠ですし。",
            "enText": "Ah, but I think I like them more when fiction is mixed in! When \nyou add in anecdotes like that, it helps keep people interested!",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 350,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": 7606902875719104676
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 5016673172546388183
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3485897502212851570,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "そのくらい慕われて、誰の記憶にも残る。そんな存在こそが英雄で！\nだから、私――",
            "enText": "Being admired like that, helps it remain in everyone's memory. \nThat kind of existence is a hero! That's why, I――",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 248,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 45,
                    "pathId": -7767998317705041311
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -8953321004870200241
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6548497874495420314,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "後世で、『英雄の物語』として語られて、はじめて！\n伝記は英雄譚になるんじゃないかなって思っていて！",
            "enText": "I think that's how over time they become a 『Tale of a Hero』! \nThat biographies eventually become heroic tales!",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 307,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "英雄の話が好きなんだな",
                    "enText": "You like heroes, huh?",
                    "nextBlock": 15
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "英雄の話が好きなんだね",
                    "enText": "You like heroes, huh?",
                    "nextBlock": 15
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 330,
                    "pathId": 3325591884096161899
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 1612510911720947262
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": -8823113319095152123
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2891182522742641386,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "あっ、その、いえ……違うんです、すみません。",
            "enText": "Ah, um, no…… that's not true, I'm sorry.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 225,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 229,
                    "pathId": -4169743076659743314
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -1447630635926204939
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1360062403942527144,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "1人で勝手に盛り上がっちゃって……\nあ、伝記の棚、そちらです。",
            "enText": "I was getting excited all on my own…… \nAh, the shelf with biographies is over there.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 226,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "？ありがとう……",
                    "enText": "? Thanks……",
                    "nextBlock": 17
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": 7679215066458150877
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -2779009075093416562
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3013329699934990575,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "いえ……ごめんなさいっ、失礼します……！",
            "enText": "No…… I'm sorry, please excuse me……!",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 193,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 188,
                    "pathId": -434540526914762660
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": 3366269402978415916
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2122896551211283322,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "一気に元気をなくしてしまった……。\n『違う』と言っていたが、あれで英雄譚が好きでないとは思えない。",
            "enText": "She suddenly became less energetic…… [That's not true] \nis what she said but, it was hard to believe that \nshe didn't based on how she acted.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 115,
                    "pathId": 1861207002316651921
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": -7667884073158467802
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": 5922054255224345202
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5784294469127396863,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "なぜ否定なんてしたのだろう？　そう考えつつも、\n今はまず、教えてもらった棚から本を探すことにした。",
            "enText": "Why did she deny it though? While thinking that, I decided to \nsearch for a book on the shelf she mentioned for now.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "pathId": -6082359213354647594,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "だいぶ読みふけってしまった。確かにフィクションも混ざって\nいそうだったが、それを差し引いても素晴らしい英雄譚だった……！",
            "enText": "I ended up reading through a lot. Like she said, a lot of fiction \nwas mixed in but, even then it was still a great heroic story……!",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 123,
            "pathId": 4826700889816820803,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "……英雄譚は、物語として語られて\nはじめて英雄譚足り得る――",
            "enText": "……when a story starts to often be told in a heroic manner, \nit becomes a heroic tale――",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 281,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 153,
                    "pathId": 7741313710314005019
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7037854602616827354,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "でも私の物語は、まだ……\nううん、もしかしたら、これからもずっと……。",
            "enText": "But my story, hasn't even…… \nNo, maybe, it won't ever……",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 384,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "すみません、貸出お願いします！",
                    "enText": "Excuse me, I'd like to borrow this!",
                    "nextBlock": 23
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": 1928679246464643280
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 5014805009860006292
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1836933162918163770,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "あっ……はいっ！　か、貸出ですねっ。\nって、その本……。",
            "enText": "Ah…… okay! You'd like to borrow it, right? \nOh, that book……",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 245,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": 7813612102893039123
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 152,
                    "pathId": -1630833418098076127
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2800682953192527208,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "……英雄譚、お好きなんですか？",
            "enText": "……do you like heroic tales?",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 156,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "英雄みたいなウマ娘を見て、影響されて",
                    "enText": "I saw a hero-like Uma Musume, so I was interested",
                    "nextBlock": 25
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 196,
                    "pathId": -9007271300754522802
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": -6452086648608667767
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5188295253765775394,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "かのウマ娘の走りが鮮烈に記憶に残っていること、\nずっとそのウマ娘を探していること……などを話した。",
            "enText": "That Uma Musume's running was vividly etched in to my mind, so I \nhad been searching for her this whole time…… is what I told her.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 196,
                    "pathId": -8352470495098537140
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 135,
                    "pathId": 2282711991028724595
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7850986499505420375,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "『英雄みたいな』ウマ娘……。",
            "enText": "『A hero-like』 Uma Musume……",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 141,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 162,
                    "pathId": 1593684912244513363
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 186,
                    "pathId": -4715568634277698816
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1917404296022998325,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "英雄だと感じてしまうくらい、\n遠目に見ても素晴らしい走りだった……ってことですよね。",
            "enText": "You couldn't help but feel like she was a hero, even if you only \nsaw her running from a distance……is what you said, right?",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 287,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 307,
                    "pathId": 112620837047675311
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": 581554622241259192
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3223503058090507905,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "そんな走りをするウマ娘が、\n今、トレセン学園にいるってことですよねっ……！",
            "enText": "An Uma Musume that can run like that, right now, is at Tracen \nAcademy is what you're saying, right……!?",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 241,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "は、はい……！",
                    "enText": "Y-yeah……!",
                    "nextBlock": 29
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 130,
                    "pathId": 4835356499347945558
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 205,
                    "pathId": -2508831699215101925
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4817248467482163913,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "……！",
            "enText": "……！",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 128,
                    "pathId": 6834473057584475531
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 140,
                    "pathId": -2925436946284549317
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 875284800774961867,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "……あ、あのっ……今日お会いしたばっかりですし、\n無理を承知でお願いするんですが！",
            "enText": "……U-um…… I know we just met today, and I'm aware it's an \nunreasonable request but!",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 304,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 194,
                    "pathId": 5770474216449340837
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 128,
                    "pathId": -1855853855764088344
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5232620868527419358,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "私に！　その『英雄探し』、手伝わせてほしいです！",
            "enText": "Can you let me help you with that 『Hero Search』!?",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 189,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ええ！？",
                    "enText": "Eeeh!?",
                    "nextBlock": 32
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": 114613761798393925
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -2451779047290348756
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4006879269341767871,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "資料探しや、英雄に関する知識には自信がありますっ！\nきっとお役に立てると思うんですが！",
            "enText": "I'm confident in my skills to search for documents and I know a \nlot about heroes! I'll definitely be helpful!",
            "nextBlock": 33,
            "origClipLength": 283,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 103,
                    "pathId": 6210233958980635347
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 242,
                    "pathId": -8579731655444951486
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6610304298313039597,
            "blockIdx": 32
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "願ってもないことではあるが、\nトレセン学園において、学生の本分は走ること。",
            "enText": "It was an offer that was incredibly beneficial to me but, when it \ncomes to Tracen Academy, shouldn't a student's priority be to run?",
            "nextBlock": 34,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": 755621062449438267
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 151,
                    "pathId": 6312256252808803397
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5371089678423894436,
            "blockIdx": 33
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "手伝ってもらうことで、ゼンノロブロイのトレーニングの\n妨げになりはしないか……そう訊ねた。",
            "enText": "I asked Zenno Rob Roy if helping me would \nget in the way of her training.",
            "nextBlock": 35,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 169,
                    "pathId": -7524049720891392003
                },
